<html>
<body>
  <span tal:replace="structure view/email_header|nothing" />
  <table width="500px">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>
       
          Dear <span tal:replace="view/data/FirstName" />,
  
	  <p>Thank you for creating a personal fundraising page. The following is the information relating to your page:</p>

	  Name: <span tal:content="view/data/Name" /> <br />
	  Description: <span tal:content="view/data/Description" /> <br />
	  Goal: <span tal:content="view/data/ExpectedRevenue" /> <br />

		  <p>You can view yor page using the following link:</p>
		  <p><a tal:attributes="href view/data/campaign/absolute_url"
			  tal:content="view/data/campaign/absolute_url"></a></p>

		  <p>You can edit yor page using the following link:</p>
		  <p><a tal:attributes="href string:${view/data/campaign/absolute_url}/edit"
			  tal:content="string:${view/data/campaign/absolute_url}/edit"></a></p>


		  <p>The site admninistrators.</p>
  
          <span tal:replace="structure view/email_footer|nothing" />
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
